      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, delivering 333hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical state is superlative: the double VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and all original VIN-matching panels, this chassis maintains its factory-spec torsional rigidity. The individual throttle bodies (ITBs) are perfectly synced, providing the instantaneous throttle response and metallic rasp that define this analog icon. Truly a showroom-quality specimen for the discerning collector.",
